Class HtmlLineContent

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sourcecoderepositorywebscraping.core.HtmlLineContent

  • public class HtmlLineContent
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents each html string line from repository url. Example of 3 instances types: 1) {content="125 lines (90 sloc)", isDirectory=false, hasTagSearchLines=true, hasTagSearchBytes=true} 2) {content=" 3.67 KB", isDirectory=false, hasTagSearchLines=false, hasTagSearchBytes=true} 3) {content="href="/fbentes/EmitesJavaJobApplicationChallenge/tree/master/IMDbQueryProject/javadoc">javadoc</a></span>", isDirectory=true, hasTagSearchLines=false, hasTagSearchBytes=false}
